{"id":491,"ayahs":[{"number":23,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ مَآ أَرْسَلْنَا مِن قَبْلِكَ فِى قَرْيَةٍۢ مِّن نَّذِيرٍ إِلَّا قَالَ مُتْرَفُوهَآ إِنَّا وَجَدْنَآ ءَابَآءَنَا عَلَىٰٓ أُمَّةٍۢ وَإِنَّا عَلَىٰٓ ءَاثَٰرِهِم مُّقْتَدُونَ","translation":"And thus it is: whenever We sent, before thy time, a warner to any community, those of its people who had lost themselves entirely in the pursuit of pleasures would always say, “Behold, we found our forefathers agreed on what to believe - and, verily, it is but in their footsteps that we follow!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4348.mp3","surahId":43,"words":[{"id":25609,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25610,"position":2,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25611,"position":3,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা পাঠিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25612,"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25613,"position":5,"arabic":"قَبْلِكَ","translation":"তোমার পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25614,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25615,"position":7,"arabic":"قَرْيَةٍۢ","translation":"কোন জনপদের","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25616,"position":8,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25617,"position":9,"arabic":"نَّذِيرٍ","translation":"সতর্ককারী","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25618,"position":10,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ব্যতীত যে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25619,"position":11,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বলেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25620,"position":12,"arabic":"مُتْرَفُوهَآ","translation":"তার বিত্তশালীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25621,"position":13,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25622,"position":14,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَآ","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25623,"position":15,"arabic":"ءَابَآءَنَا","translation":"আমাদের বাপ-দাদাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25624,"position":16,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25625,"position":17,"arabic":"أُمَّةٍۢ","translation":"(এই) মতাদর্শের","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25626,"position":18,"arabic":"وَإِنَّا","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25627,"position":19,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25628,"position":20,"arabic":"ءَاثَـٰرِهِم","translation":"তাদের পদাঙ্কসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25629,"position":21,"arabic":"مُّقْتَدُونَ","translation":"অনুসরণকারী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/043_023_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25630,"position":22,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"۞ قَٰلَ أَوَلَوْ جِئْتُكُم بِأَهْدَىٰ مِمَّا وَجَدتُّمْ عَلَيْهِ ءَابَآءَكُمْ ۖ قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّا بِمَآ أُرْسِلْتُم بِهِۦ كَٰفِرُونَ","translation":"[Whereupon each prophet] would say, “Why, even though I bring you guidance better than that which you found your forefathers believing in?” - [to which] the others would reply, “Behold, we deny that there is any truth in [what you claim to be] your messages!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4349.mp3","surahId":43,"words":[{"id":26673,"positio