l":"wbw/043_031_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33360,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْقَرْيَتَيْنِ","translation":"(মাক্কা ও তায়েফের) দু'টি জনপদের","audioUrl":"wbw/043_031_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33361,"position":10,"arabic":"عَظِيمٍ","translation":"(যে) বড় বা প্রতিপত্তিশালীর\"","audioUrl":"wbw/043_031_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33362,"position":11,"arabic":"٣١","translation":"(৩১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":32,"arabic":"أَهُمْ يَقْسِمُونَ رَحْمَتَ رَبِّكَ ۚ نَحْنُ قَسَمْنَا بَيْنَهُم مَّعِيشَتَهُمْ فِى ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا ۚ وَرَفَعْنَا بَعْضَهُمْ فَوْقَ بَعْضٍۢ دَرَجَٰتٍۢ لِّيَتَّخِذَ بَعْضُهُم بَعْضًۭا سُخْرِيًّۭا ۗ وَرَحْمَتُ رَبِّكَ خَيْرٌۭ مِّمَّا يَجْمَعُونَ","translation":"But is it they who distribute thy Sustainer’s grace? [Nay, as] it is We who distribute their means of livelihood among them in the life of this world, and raise some of them by degrees above others, to the end that they might avail themselves of one another’s help - [so, too, it is We who bestow gifts of the spirit upon whomever We will]: and this thy Sustainer’s grace is better than all [the worldly wealth] that they may amass.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4357.mp3","surahId":43,"words":[{"id":34402,"position":1,"arabic":"أَهُمْ","translation":"(তাদেরকে বলো) তারা কি","audioUrl":"wbw/043_032_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34403,"position":2,"arabic":"يَقْسِمُونَ","translation":"বণ্টন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/043_032_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34404,"position":3,"arabic":"رَحْمَتَ","translation":"(দয়া-করুণা) অনুগ্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/043_032_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34405,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ ۚ","translation":"তোমার রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/043_032_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34407,"position":5,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","translation":"আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/043_032_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34408,"position":6,"arabic":"قَسَمْنَا","translation":"বণ্টন করি","